{"tid":951664,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"做左咁耐香港人,都唔知原來有樣野叫香港飯","createTime":"2018-12-22T13:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T18:06:14.000Z","uid":138834,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"195445306a868edc86c50b668274a3848d5a2f66","tid":951664,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://blogimg.goo.ne.jp/user_image/54/d4/23357df8fa15fd8ec9922ec60829622e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblogimg.goo.ne.jp%2Fuser_image%2F54%2Fd4%2F23357df8fa15fd8ec9922ec60829622e.jpg&h=02f0562f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n丼物欄第5個<br />\n查左查,原來個樣係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/B0di053CMAAmhx_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FB0di053CMAAmhx_.jpg&h=32723f2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n應該係回鍋肉炒椰菜加蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下次去旅行試下咩味"},{"pid":"9ef28d8a68fdad01310ece95e3ab0263128acbd2","tid":951664,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:53:44.000Z","msg":"睇錯,D菜應該係黃芽白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcb6c9275abcde85439d91433f4ad34a45941e6","tid":951664,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:53:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4e730f696efede2f91aef10b6035f48f9fa2bdc","tid":951664,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"H ong K ong Rice"},{"pid":"7a23b99410a3d6cfd2835e4bbc7e1af9b5e43437","tid":951664,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"瑞士夠冇瑞士雞翼啦"},{"pid":"91d6e98c72454c77feb2ce3d94e4ad4be295e760","tid":951664,"uid":23315,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score